====== H724: אֲרוּכָה (ʼărûwkâh) ======

===== Source =====

or   ; feminine passive participle of  H748  (in the sense of   to soundness);

===== Meaning =====

restoring wholeness  (literally or figuratively)

===== Definitions =====

  - restoring
  - wholeness

===== Usage =====

health, made up, perfected.
